              <text><citation jurisdiction="nz">Section <extref href="DLM424333">707A</extref> of the principal Act</citation> (as substituted by <citation jurisdiction="nz">section <extref href="DLM261841">67(1)</extref> of the <leg-title href="DLM261626">Local Government Amendment Act 1992</leg-title></citation>) is amended by omitting from <citation jurisdiction="nz">subsection <extref href="DLM424333">(2)</extref></citation> the expression <amend.in quote="1"><citation jurisdiction="nz">Part XLIVB</citation></amend.in>, and substituting the expression <amend.in quote="1"><citation jurisdiction="nz">Part 44C</citation></amend.in>.</text>
